            <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Accessibility statement for Strengths Based Needs Assessments</h1>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                This page only contains information about the Strengths Based Needs Assessments service, available at:
                <a href="https://strengths-based-needs-assessments.hmpps.service.justice.gov.uk" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state">
                    https://strengths-based-needs-assessments.hmpps.service.justice.gov.uk/
                </a>
            </p>

            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Using this service</h2>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                This service is run by HMPPS Digital Services.
                We want as many people as possible to be able to use this service.
            </p>
            <p class="govuk-body">For example, that means you should be able to:</p>
