                <li>get from the start of the service to the end using just a keyboard</li>
                <li>get from the start of the service to the end using speech recognition software</li>
                <li>listen to the service using a screen reader (including the most recent versions of JAWS, NVDA and
                    VoiceOver)
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="govuk-body">We've also made the text in the service as simple as possible to understand.</p>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                <a href="https://mcmw.abilitynet.org.uk/" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state">AbilityNet</a>
                has advice on making your device easier to use if you have a disability.
            </p>

